# VibeShield Security Rules
Every HTTP Handler Must use `vibeShield()` wrapper (TS) or `VibeShieldASGIMiddleware` (Python) and define `validationSchema`.
Forbidden: `eval()`, `pickle.loads()`, `shell=True`, hardcoded secrets.
Always use `safeJsonParse`, `enforceSafeUrl`, and `safeExec`.
